  "name": "Medical Release Negative Emotion Sensing",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Medical.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This is a perfected sensory ninjutsu based on the principles from \"Kagura's Mind Eye\". This jutsu digs further instead targeting a creature's emotions to track and keep notice of them from up to 100 feet away. You are able to immediately tell the emotional state or intentions of a creature within range. A Creature who attempts to hide these emotions must make a Deception check against your Ninjutsu Save DC. You can sense discomfort, enjoyment, anger, and even killing intent.</p>",
